data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat in the heart of Milton with a BRAND-NEW ROOF, FRESH PAINT THROUGHOUT, LOCATED ON 1.59 ACRES! This enchanting property offers the perfect blend of serenity, elegance, and comfort, nestled on a sprawling 1.59-acre lot adorned with lush greenery and mature trees. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of pristine hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout the main living spaces and bedrooms. The spacious kitchen is a culinary haven, offering ample counter space, beautiful wood cabinets, an adjoining dining area with a captivating fireplace that invites cozy gatherings on chilly evenings, and natural light that pours in through large windows, illuminating the heart of the home and creating a delightful atmosphere for every meal. With three generously sized bedrooms, this home offers versatile living arrangements for families, professionals, or those seeking a peaceful retreat. The primary bedroom features an ensuite bath, providing a private oasis for relaxation and self-care. An additional well-appointed bathroom serves the other bedrooms and guests, offering convenience and comfort for all. Car enthusiasts and hobbyists will appreciate the ATTACHED TWO-CAR GARAGE PLUS A 1,080 SF DETACHED WORKSHOP, which provides secure parking and ample storage space for your vehicles and belongings. The property's exterior is a nature lover's paradise, offering endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply unwinding amid tranquility. Enjoy the view from your screened porch, host summer barbecues on the expansive lawn, create a picturesque garden, or design your outdoor oasis where the possibilities are as limitless as your imagination. Located in Milton's sought-after Arcadia Mill area, this home perfectly balances rural living and urban convenience. Enjoy the peace and privacy of a large lot while being just a short drive away from local amenities, shopping, schools, parks, recreation, and I-10.
